      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 41,
      "message": "The question would be as this would create tight coupling to an specific library, if in the future there is the possibility to use a different JPA library that many not support this functionality (to keep the code portable)?   This is just a question.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
        "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
